<b>Song Stacking - </b>12/3/01 6:15:52 PM<br>~ <b>Qeynestri</b><blockquote>While the reasons this song stacks with the same song from another bard may be ellusive, think of it like this: This song is NOT a duration spell.  It only gives mana for the tick that it is sung.  It also has NO icon in the buff window, so you only know that it is working from the song message - &quot;Your mind clears.&quot; <br><br>Something else to keep in mind - it takes 3 seconds for the song to take effect once begun and 6 seconds for it to hit the next tick if sung continuously.  With little lag and a fast connection, one can stop and start the song over and get the effect to hit again before it would normally if it was sung continuously.  In this way, one can deliver more mana back over an extended period of downtime =).</blockquote></td></tr><tr bgcolor="#eeeeee"><td>
